{"title":"平原浪涌","authors":["刘益善"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":8,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原浪涌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘益善"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大浪涌来，碧青色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大浪涌来，金黄色的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在季候风的鼓动下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾尽了九天的河水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荡动起来荡动起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命在这里复活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉静在这里消亡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从天边来，向天边去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我不息的心潮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向着强悍的父亲滚动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲是平原上的岛屿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着些许的留恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作一刹的缓冲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再向前推过去推过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走向成熟走向收获"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要云彩不停止飘动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有无垠的浪涌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原警醒着躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搏动着儿子的希求和企盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向父亲扬起手臂奔去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲是平原的桅樯"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}